The system is literally unable to deliver electricity to people it’s supposed to serve without risking killing those same people.
Private industry in California could have invested in upgraded power lines, and even burying lines where practical so they don’t spark in high winds.
We still have the ability to vote out people who are owned by big money.
Vote anyway, for the candidates you think are good or at least not as bad.
